<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="war-n">war <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɔː(r)/    美 /wɔːr/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>战争：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>World War II broke out in 1939.
第二次世界大战爆发于1939年。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a trade war
贸易战</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-war-with">at war (with)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(与…) 交战：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This was a time when the two countries were at war.
此时正值两国交战之际。</p><footer>人教② – 1</footer></div>

<h3 id="declare-war-on">declare war on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对…宣战</strong>  </p></div>